          <h3>Empowering local and regional</h3>
          <p class="txt-xl">The European Committee of the Regions (CoR) is the voice of regions and cities in the European Union (EU). By empowering local and regional elected politicians to shape the EU legislation, we pursue our mission to create a Union closer to its citizens and built on their needs. </p>
          <a href="">Learn about our local and regional</a>
        </div>
        <div class="cor-grid">
